;background-color: #F2F2F2;height: 100% !important;width: 100% !important;\">\n        <center>\n            <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" height=\"100%\" width=\"100%\" id=\"bodyTable\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;background-color: #F2F2F2;height: 100% !important;width: 100% !important;\">\n                <tr>\n                    <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" id=\"bodyCell\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 20px;border-top: 0;height: 100% !important;width: 100% !important;\">\n                        <!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE // -->\n                        <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;border: 0;\">\n                            <tr>\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                                    <!-- BEGIN PREHEADER // -->\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templatePreheader\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;background-color: #FFFFFF;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\n                                        <tr>\n                                        \t<td valign=\"top\" class=\"preheaderContainer\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n        <tr>\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                    <tbody><tr>\n\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding: 9px 18px;text-align: justify;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 11px;line-height: 125%;\">\n\n                            <div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">\n<div>Hi sunshine,</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>Hope you are having Happy week. Here is the invitation to the Happy Hearts Gala on&nbsp;<span class=\"aBn\" data-term=\"goog_295460079\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #CCCCCC;border-bottom-style: dashed;border-bottom-width: 1px;position: relative;top: -2px;z-index: 0;\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"aQJ\" style=\"position:relative; top:2px; z-index:-1\">June 19th</span></span>, which this year will be very special and meaningful.&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">It is hard to believe that this year marks the 10th anniversary of the devastating 2004 tsunami which I was blessed to survive,&nbsp;therefore it will be an extra special gala. We will celebrate the 85 resilient disaster-proof schools that have been rebuilt and the happiness that they have brought to 46,000 children in seven countries that have been impacted by natural disasters. Our goal is to open our 100th school by&nbsp;<span class=\"aBn\" data-term=\"goog_295460080\" style=\"border-bottom-color: #CCCCCC;border-bottom-style: dashed;border-bottom-width: 1px;position: relative;top: -2px;z-index: 0;\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"aQJ\" style=\"position:relative; top:2px; z-index:-1\">December 26th 2014</span></span>, on the day of the anniversary.</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">This night will also be extremely special because of our incredible honorees. Bill Clinton, the 42nd President of United States,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://happyheartsfund.us2.list-manage.com/track/click?u=c80ab18b6ed45d0c817ea32b1&id=6f86c0c9db&e=1835002b47\" style=\"color: #1155CC;word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\" target=\"_blank\">will.i.am</a>&nbsp;and apl.de.ap from the Black Eyed Peas and United Airlines. Each of our honorees focus on helping children and communities after natural disasters. I have attached the invitation for you below.</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">Will you be able to join us during this meaningful and unforgettable event please? Will you help us to rebuild 100&nbsp;resilient disaster-proof schools this year for children who are forgotten for years after natural disasters? Would you help us to bring hope to children who lost it as their voices have not been heard please?&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">Lots of Love, Light and Laughter&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #222222;font-family: arial, sans-serif;line-height: normal;\">P.</div>\n\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                    </table>\n                                    <!-- // END PREHEADER -->\n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                                    <!-- BEGIN HEADER // -->\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateHeader\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;background-color: #FFFFFF;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\n                                        <tr>\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"headerContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnImageBlock\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n    <tbody class=\"mcnImageBlockOuter\">\n            <tr>\n                <td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding: 9px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\" class=\"mcnImageBlockInner\">\n                    <table align=\"left\" width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"mcnImageContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                        <tbody><tr>\n                            <td class=\"mcnImageContent\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-right: 9px;padding-left: 9px;padding-top: 0;padding-bottom: 0;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n\n                                    <a href=\"http://happyheartsfund.us2.list-manage.com/track/click?u=c80ab18b6ed45d0c817ea32b1&id=59fda8a8fa&e=1835002b47\" title=\"\" class=\"\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                                        <img align=\"left\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://gallery.mailchimp.com/c80ab18b6ed45d0c817ea32b1/images/516a907b-9f94-4f7f-af2e-1d41787e8880.jpg\" width=\"564\" style=\"max-width: 1152px;padding-bottom: 0;display: inline !important;vertical-align: bottom;border: 0;outline: none;text-decoration: none;-ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;\" class=\"mcnImage\">\n                                    </a>\n\n                            </td>\n                        </tr>\n                    </tbody></table>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table><table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"100%\" class=\"mcnTextBlock\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n    <tbody class=\"mcnTextBlockOuter\">\n        <tr>\n            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextBlockInner\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n\n                <table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" class=\"mcnTextContentContainer\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                    <tbody><tr>\n\n                        <td valign=\"top\" class=\"mcnTextContent\" style=\"padding-top: 9px;padding-right: 18px;padding-bottom: 9px;padding-left: 18px;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 150%;text-align: left;\">\n\n                            <h1 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 40px;line-height: 50px;letter-spacing: -1px;text-align: center;color: #606060 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;\">INVITATION</h1>\n\n<h2 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 26px;line-height: 32px;letter-spacing: -0.75px;text-align: center;color: #404040 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;\">Happy Hearts Fund Gala</h2>\n<span style=\"color: #606060;font-family: helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;\">&nbsp;</span>\n\n<h3 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 18px;line-height: 22px;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: center;color: #606060 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;\">Celebrating the achievements we have created together 10 years after the Indian Ocean Tsunami.</h3>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\"><br>\nLifetime Achievement Award Honoree<br>\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h4 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;color: #808080 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: normal;\">BILL CLINTON</h4>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\">FOUNDER OF THE CLINTON FOUNDATION<br>\n&amp; 42nd PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES<br>\nFor his leadership and life saving work ensuring that children&nbsp;and communities are not forgotten after&nbsp;disaster strikes<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nHonored Partner Award Honoree<br>\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h4 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;color: #808080 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: normal;\">UNITED AIRLINES</h4>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\">MR. JEFF SMISEK, CHAIRMAN OF THE BOARD, PRESIDENT &amp; CEO<br>\nFor their continued support and partnership enabling HHF team members to conduct&nbsp;important site visits to&nbsp;the countries and schools that we support<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nSpirit Award Honoree<br>\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h4 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 16px;text-align: center;color: #808080 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;line-height: 125%;letter-spacing: normal;\">APL.DE.AP &amp; WILL.I.AM</h4>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\">For utilizing their talents and showing commitment to children and communities impacted by&nbsp;natural disasters in the Philippines and other countries<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nWith special music appearances<br>\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<h3 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 18px;line-height: 22px;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: center;color: #606060 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;\">Thursday June 19th 2014<span style=\"font-size:13px; line-height:1.6em; text-align:left\">&nbsp;</span></h3>\n\n<h3 class=\"null\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 18px;line-height: 22px;letter-spacing: -0.5px;text-align: center;color: #606060 !important;display: block;font-style: normal;font-weight: bold;\">Cipriani 42nd Street, New York</h3>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\">Cocktails at 6pm, Dinner and Program at 7:00pm<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nClick&nbsp;<a href=\"http://happyheartsfund.us2.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=c80ab18b6ed45d0c817ea32b1&id=7313008556&e=1835002b47\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;color: #6DC6DD;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">here</a>&nbsp;to see the impact that your support has made!<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\n<u>To become a sponsor or purchase tables/tickets, please contact:&nbsp;</u><br>\n<u>Sue Veres Royal at&nbsp;<a style=\"word-wrap: break-word;color: #6DC6DD;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">(347) 406-3835</a></u><br>\n<u>or&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sue@happyheartsfund.org\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;color: #6DC6DD;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">sue@happyheartsfund.org</a></u><br>\n&nbsp;</div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\"><em><span style=\"font-size:12px\">The mission of Happy Hearts Fund is to rebuild schools and restore hope and opportunity in the lives of children after natural disasters. We work during the period after emergency response is complete, implementing sustainable practices to ensure a lasting impact.<br>\n&nbsp;<br>\nGlobally, Happy Hearts Fund is active in seven&nbsp;countries and has built/rebuilt 85 schools<br>\n&nbsp;and kindergartens. Since inception in 2006, our programs have benefitted more than 46,000 children and 490,000 community members.</span></em></div>\n\n<div style=\"color: #606060;font-family: Helvetica;font-size: 15px;line-height: 22px;text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<br>\n<a href=\"http://happyheartsfund.us2.list-manage1.com/track/click?u=c80ab18b6ed45d0c817ea32b1&id=a6e5980c08&e=1835002b47\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;color: #6DC6DD;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;font-weight: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">www.happyheartsfund.org</a></div>\n\n                        </td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody></table>\n\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                    </table>\n                                    <!-- // END HEADER -->\n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">\n                                    <!-- BEGIN BODY // -->\n                                    <table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"600\" id=\"templateBody\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;background-color: #FFFFFF;border-top: 0;border-bottom: 0;\">\n                                        <tr>\n                                            <td valign=\"top\" class=\"bodyContainer\" style=\"mso-table-lspace: 0pt;mso-table-rspace: 0pt;-ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\"></td>\n                                        </tr>\n                                    </table>\n                                    <!-- // END BODY -->\n                                </td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td ali